WEBVTT

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:39.799
Gu Zhantian,

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.599
I'll give you one last chance.

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:43.959
Get lost,

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.439
or die.

00:01:47.799 --> 00:01:48.599
So noisy.

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:50.439
Guess there's nothing to talk about then.

00:02:18.439 --> 00:02:20.000
The protagonist really can do whatever he wants.

00:02:20.120 --> 00:02:21.639
How could you mortal things

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:23.439
ever hurt me?

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:25.240
Get him!

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:16.639
Jealous?

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:18.719
This is the power of the protagonist.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:21.000
Peak combat strength,

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:23.439
surrounded by beauties.

00:03:26.360 --> 00:03:27.120
And me?

00:03:27.479 --> 00:03:29.080
I'm the guy getting killed.

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.000
A villain.

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:33.719
Dead.

00:03:45.439 --> 00:03:46.240
Lu Chengwen.

00:03:47.120 --> 00:03:49.240
This is already your sixth failure.

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:50.919
Furthermore,

00:03:50.919 --> 00:03:53.479
you didn't even survive the first chapter.

00:03:55.879 --> 00:03:56.680
Fate-Defier.

00:03:56.919 --> 00:03:58.639
I don't think it's my fault!

00:03:58.879 --> 00:03:59.960
Didn't I transmigrate into an

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:01.479
Urban Male Power Fantasy?

00:04:01.599 --> 00:04:03.199
Then why does the male lead have superpowers?

00:04:03.199 --> 00:04:03.439
No,

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:04.520
this is way too ridiculous!

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:05.599
A villain like me

00:04:05.599 --> 00:04:07.000
has absolutely no room to survive!

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:10.080
Alright,

00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:11.879
stop complaining.

00:04:12.039 --> 00:04:13.719
Don't blame me for not warning you.

00:04:15.439 --> 00:04:17.000
If you fail one more time,

00:04:18.439 --> 00:04:20.079
you will disappear forever.

00:04:20.480 --> 00:04:22.480
You won't be able to return to the real world.

00:04:25.199 --> 00:04:25.480
Wait,

00:04:25.480 --> 00:04:26.079
something this important,

00:04:26.079 --> 00:04:27.000
why are you only saying it now?

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:27.720
I've already died six times!

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:28.600
And you're just telling me?

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:30.879
You never asked me.

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:32.439
I've died six times!

00:04:32.439 --> 00:04:33.839
I think you shouldn't be called Fate-Defier,

00:04:33.839 --> 00:04:35.079
you should just be called a sneaky bastard.

00:04:35.319 --> 00:04:36.879
You're unbelievably shady.

00:04:39.399 --> 00:04:40.199
Fine.

00:04:42.399 --> 00:04:44.120
Since I can't beat him in a head-on fight,

00:04:44.199 --> 00:04:45.639
I'll just lay low, okay?

00:04:45.839 --> 00:04:46.839
I'll show you

00:04:46.839 --> 00:04:49.120
what it means that if heaven didn't birth me, Lu Chengwen,

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:51.319
the art of laying low would be an endless night!

00:04:56.839 --> 00:04:57.639
Bring it on.

00:05:10.639 --> 00:05:11.879
I'm really cursed.

00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:14.199
This garbage plot insists that I

00:05:14.199 --> 00:05:15.240
fight this male lead over a woman.

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:16.399
Isn't that just asking for death?

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:18.480
I need to hurry up and ruin this engagement.

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:19.319
And stay far away from

00:05:19.519 --> 00:05:20.319
Leng Qingqiu.

00:05:27.079 --> 00:05:28.639
That sounds like Leng Qingqiu's voice.

00:05:40.279 --> 00:05:42.120
She really haunts me like a ghost.

00:05:42.439 --> 00:05:44.199
I just said I needed to get away from Leng Qingqiu,

00:05:44.439 --> 00:05:45.600
and here she is.

00:05:46.519 --> 00:05:47.680
This look...

00:05:48.040 --> 00:05:49.240
it's my first time seeing it.

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:57.879
This Lu Chengwen...

00:05:57.879 --> 00:05:58.839
what is he staring at?

00:05:59.399 --> 00:06:01.199
He must be the one who tied me up here.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:06.639
Why is she tied up here?

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:09.319
I was too focused on Gu Zhantian before,

00:06:09.399 --> 00:06:10.800
I didn't even look closely at Leng Qingqiu.

00:06:11.279 --> 00:06:13.199
As expected of Haicheng's number one beauty,

00:06:13.399 --> 00:06:15.079
she's so alluring even when tied up.

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:16.240
What is that sound?

00:06:29.519 --> 00:06:30.319
Scumbag.

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:31.879
You think tying me up here

00:06:31.879 --> 00:06:33.000
will make me marry you?

00:06:33.279 --> 00:06:34.000
Disgusting.

00:06:34.399 --> 00:06:35.720
I didn't tie you up.

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:37.079
I'm here to save you.

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.519
I heard it again.

00:06:38.879 --> 00:06:39.920
His lips didn't move.

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:41.240
How is he making a sound?

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:43.439
Could it be that just by looking into his eyes,

00:06:43.639 --> 00:06:45.399
I can hear his inner thoughts?

00:06:45.959 --> 00:06:47.600
I will never get engaged to you.

00:06:51.079 --> 00:06:52.040
Good, good.

00:06:53.319 --> 00:06:54.920
We're not a good match anyway.

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:55.519
This engagement,

00:06:56.120 --> 00:06:57.040
let's just call it off.

00:06:59.079 --> 00:07:01.279
You should hurry up and be Gu Zhantian's backup,

00:07:01.639 --> 00:07:02.879
hand over your family fortune to him,

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:04.480
and live happily as his wife.

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:06.000
That way, I'll have some peace too.

00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:08.199
Me, Gu Zhantian's backup?

00:07:08.839 --> 00:07:10.639
And giving away my family fortune?

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:11.839
Lu Chengwen!

00:07:12.199 --> 00:07:13.399
How dare you insult me!

00:07:14.279 --> 00:07:16.000
When did I insult you?

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:21.000
Miss Leng,

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:22.000
I'm really sorry

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:23.079
for being so presumptuous...

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:24.800
Young Master!

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:27.040
You...

00:07:27.399 --> 00:07:28.600
Why are you here?

00:07:31.839 --> 00:07:32.639
Zhao Gang,

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:33.879
did you tie her up?

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.439
I was just afraid

00:07:35.600 --> 00:07:36.920
Miss Leng would run away from the wedding,

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:38.480
so I made some arrangements.

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:42.319
Why is my lackey so dim-witted?

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.439
If Leng Qingqiu's dad sees this,

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:45.920
he'll definitely break ties with me!

00:07:46.839 --> 00:07:47.839
He didn't know about this.

00:07:48.079 --> 00:07:49.399
I wrongly accused him.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:54.399
Dad

00:07:54.399 --> 00:07:55.240
Save me

00:07:55.240 --> 00:07:56.079
Save me, quick

00:07:58.199 --> 00:07:59.639
Just what I feared

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:02.240
Uncle Leng

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:02.959
This

00:08:04.399 --> 00:08:05.199
Zhao Gang

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:06.000
Ah

00:08:07.639 --> 00:08:09.240
Didn't I say to lock Qingqiu up in a

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:10.639
hidden place and keep her under control?

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:12.600
How could you let Chengwen worry about such a small thing?

00:08:13.319 --> 00:08:14.120
Dad

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:15.120
What do you mean?

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:16.399
You arranged this?

00:08:16.519 --> 00:08:18.000
How could you do this to me?

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:19.079
Shut up

00:08:19.319 --> 00:08:21.199
You've dragged out this engagement for so long with your fuss

00:08:21.199 --> 00:08:22.879
Our Leng family can't afford to lose this much face

00:08:23.199 --> 00:08:24.000
Lose face?

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:24.920
You tied me up here

00:08:24.920 --> 00:08:26.079
and you don't think that's losing face?

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:27.519
You

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:31.199
Is Leng Qingqiu really this pitiful?

00:08:31.439 --> 00:08:33.840
Outside, she's a powerful female business tycoon

00:08:33.919 --> 00:08:36.320
At home, she's just a pawn for marriage

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:38.200
I feel a bit sorry for you

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:39.639
I don't need your sympathy

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:41.120
You're no good either

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:42.039
Leng Qingqiu

00:08:42.279 --> 00:08:43.679
How are you speaking to Chengwen?

00:08:44.039 --> 00:08:44.480
Chengwen

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:45.879
Don't stoop to her level

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:48.120
I really can't stand watching this anymore

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:49.840
Let me help you teach this old fox a lesson

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:53.120
But I still need to make you hate me more

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:54.039
Uncle Leng

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:56.320
Your Leng family wants to marry into ours

00:08:56.679 --> 00:08:57.840
and this is your attitude?

00:08:58.279 --> 00:09:01.399
Tying up my fiancee like a sacrifice

00:09:01.639 --> 00:09:03.519
It's really unpresentable

00:09:06.039 --> 00:09:07.039
However

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:08.879
Qingqiu looking like this right now

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:10.919
actually has a unique charm

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:12.039
What a pity

00:09:13.399 --> 00:09:15.000
my taste has changed now

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:17.120
I like

00:09:19.039 --> 00:09:20.440
the pure and cute type

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:24.279
Let me ask you

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:26.279
is my face punchable enough?

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:28.639
He's doing it on purpose

00:09:29.639 --> 00:09:30.399
Chengwen

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:31.840
Don't overthink it

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.840
I'm already overthinking it

00:09:34.039 --> 00:09:35.879
What I like is the kind of

00:09:35.879 --> 00:09:37.720
precious jewel pampered in the palm

00:09:37.919 --> 00:09:40.840
not this kind of tied-up livestock waiting to be slaughtered

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:43.159
I think our two families'

00:09:43.159 --> 00:09:45.279
business dealings and cooperation

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:46.120
can also be put on hold

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:47.679
Let's all cool down a bit

00:09:47.919 --> 00:09:48.519
No

00:09:48.519 --> 00:09:49.320
Leng Tianhao

00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:50.679
Does it sting?

00:09:50.919 --> 00:09:53.200
This is the price for looking down on your own daughter

00:09:54.399 --> 00:09:55.120
Chengwen

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.519
I was too hasty

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.200
I shouldn't have treated Qingqiu like this

00:09:58.200 --> 00:09:58.679
Zhao Gang, see the guest out

00:09:58.679 --> 00:09:59.840
Let's not talk about cooperation

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:01.519
This way, please

00:10:17.039 --> 00:10:18.279
What beautiful hands

00:10:18.639 --> 00:10:19.720
ruined like this

00:10:24.799 --> 00:10:25.600
Thank you

00:10:27.799 --> 00:10:29.120
Her tone isn't right

00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:30.799
Why does it seem like she doesn't hate me as much?

00:10:31.039 --> 00:10:31.840
No way

00:10:32.039 --> 00:10:32.879
The plan can't fall apart

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:37.480
Don't flatter yourself

00:10:38.039 --> 00:10:41.600
I just don't want my

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:43.360
plaything

00:10:44.679 --> 00:10:46.200
to be broken

00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:52.519
You don't have much charm

00:10:52.799 --> 00:10:54.639
Compared to the girl who accompanied me last night

00:10:55.639 --> 00:10:56.480
you're far worse

00:10:56.759 --> 00:10:57.559
Plaything?

00:10:57.759 --> 00:10:58.559
Lu Chengwen

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:00.440
A leopard really can't change its spots

00:11:00.759 --> 00:11:02.000
Please rest assured, Young Master Lu

00:11:02.399 --> 00:11:05.240
I've never had any improper thoughts about you

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:06.600
As for today's matter

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:08.399
thank you for your care

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:09.919
That's good

00:11:13.759 --> 00:11:14.559
Lu Chengwen

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:16.559
I won't let you off

00:11:17.759 --> 00:11:18.600
Done

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:20.039
Now Leng Qingqiu

00:11:20.039 --> 00:11:21.799
should never want to see me again

00:11:32.039 --> 00:11:32.879
This aura

00:11:33.559 --> 00:11:34.840
Could it be that he's here?

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:56.519
This...

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:59.679
Did you just touch her?